{"tid":900576,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"員工植入晶片成趨勢 辦公室內舉動盡在掌握中","createTime":"2018-11-13T10:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T01:09:42.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f1cb4f4bd58e5b5a85c3eef0bf0163995568c3f1","tid":900576,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"英國有公司以「提升科技保安」為由，計劃在未來為僱員植入晶片，防止未經授權人士接觸機密文件，並已與瑞士的生物科技公司商討相關操作。技術上公司只需在僱員身上植入約為一顆米粒大小的晶片，情況就如現時主人為寵物植入晶片一樣。<br />\n瑞士的公司「Biohax」正與英國多間律師樓及金融機構商議，為僱員植入一顆約為白米大小、價值約150英鎊（約1,530港元）的晶片，以提升保安，防止他們進入限制範圍。<br />\n報道指，可植入人體的晶片使用近場通訊技術（NFC），亦即與非接觸式信用卡的技術相同，而晶片本身與現時使用的寵物晶片為同一類。植入晶片後，公司可限制僱員進入部份區域、員工也可以用體內的晶片，到飯堂買食物、進入大廈或使用打印機等。<br />\n「Biohax」負責人奧斯特蘭（Jowan &Ouml;sterlund）表示︰「這些公司都有處理敏感的文件，不可以丟失、外泄或忘掉它們，它們永遠都要有一個終極備份。」<br />\n奧特蘭斯表示，明白非每個人都想植入晶片，不過他相信凡事都需要經歷一個「學習曲線」（learning curve），又表示若是政府提出植入晶片的建議，他倒明白為什麼會令人反感。<br />\n消息指，英國一間僱有數以萬計員工的金融機構可能成為此項目的先行者。而在瑞典，目前已有4,000人植有晶片，當中有85人是旅遊公司「Tui」的僱員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181112/large/1542015958_5d3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181112%2Flarge%2F1542015958_5d3f.jpg&h=d124635b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奧斯特蘭（左）表示，晶片可讓公司限制任何人。<br />\n英國《每日電訊報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181113/58903932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181113%2F58903932&d=YnhgAe5tbPrEvEKdRa5CslKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=f3476b1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181113%2F58903932&h=6401e383\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181113/58903932</a>"},{"pid":"e353bf49db62f48d9becc45be76436e964ccd0be","tid":900576,"uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:48:49.000Z","msg":"slave<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd43878d1e9474231b7073006b38d72cd261376","tid":900576,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e066686f643cb676deb6ccb77a6e5578ea1528b1","tid":900576,"uid":19454,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/15/161811_25096c4e6ee714228cbc517b477f3414.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F15%2F161811_25096c4e6ee714228cbc517b477f3414.gif&h=abbfa06e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a3bc525560275c4adc62dcf3692e0821b321b1e","tid":900576,"uid":213167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a366f2c240ecf1709df8843dd5c3ea9eb58911","tid":900576,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/112648_485fc3d2d1d7936bbfd233b1b1d6df46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F112648_485fc3d2d1d7936bbfd233b1b1d6df46.png&h=9c9f5cff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba63c6ec8e98ba5847aa15d9a38359e8770ff87f","tid":900576,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"汪汪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b913a9f1be5c669bc2e152bdddd6a550b4af67a","tid":900576,"uid":22675,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:54:21.000Z","msg":"六百六十六 (666)<br />\n「他又叫眾人，無論大小、貧富、自主的、為奴的，都在右手上或是在額上受一個印記。除了那受印記，有了獸名或有獸名數目的，都不得作買賣。在這裡有智慧，凡有聰明的，可以算計獸的數目；因為這是人的數目，他的數目是六百六十六。」（啟十三16-18）"},{"pid":"67792efaba75c12209794adef9327e64174ee391","tid":900576,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:54:24.000Z","msg":"冇biometric同 vital sign monitoring 功能，一粒垃圾"},{"pid":"46535f51226e5af9c5cf049cc836beb303e9e058","tid":900576,"uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:54:59.000Z","msg":"在此我必須提醒大家，千萬不能接受獸印，有人可能會欺騙你，說接微晶片和接受獸印是兩回事，但根據聖經，就是同樣的事！因為聖經說：「又有第三位天使接著他們，大聲說：『若有人拜獸和獸像，在額上或在手上受了印記(植入晶片)，這人也必喝神大怒的酒；此酒斟在神忿怒的杯中，純一不雜。他要在聖天使和羔 羊面前，在火與硫磺之中受痛苦。他受痛苦的煙往上冒，直到永永遠遠。那些拜獸和獸像，受他名之印記的，晝夜不得安寧。』聖徒的忍耐就在此；他們是守神誡命 和耶穌真道的。」（啟十四9-12）接受獸印就等於拜獸和獸像，結局就是永遠在燒著硫磺的火湖裡受痛苦。 <br />\n但以理文（Daniel Man）<br />\n在1987年，一位名叫但以理文的猶太人，已開始從事將微型晶片植入皮膚下面的發展工作。他渴望為每個以色列人植入微型晶片，以致所有綁架和恐怖活動因此結束，因為到時每個人的位置都可以透過手提電話發射塔（cellular phone towers）或人造衛星即時準確地確定。這實在是一個打擊罪案的有效措施！ <br />\n1999年12月美國一家電訊公司（Applied Digital Solution）成功取得一種名為「數碼天使」的產品專利。「數碼天使」是一種植入體的微型數碼監察儀，能夠發出和接收數據，以致植入者的位置能持續被全球定位衛星系統偵察，有助尋回失蹤的攀山者、孩童或政要等。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">然而，類似技術若被殘暴的敵基督政權利用，所有受獸印的人就會失去自由，因為他們就算走到天涯海角，也會被找到，無法逃離獸的魔掌。</span>"},{"pid":"2f0d970ddd6874025bf701df6b8158960dbc5c4f","tid":900576,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"其實目前這計畫已經在實施了，就拿台灣目前的「悠遊卡」來講好了，<br />\n<br />\n據維基百科說：「悠遊卡（EasyCard）是通用於大台北地區的非接觸式交通電子票證系統智慧卡，使用RFID技術（飛利浦的MIFARE技術），由台北智慧卡票證公司發行，類似香港的八達通卡、JR東日本的Suica卡、JR西日本的ICOCA卡等，可用於搭乘捷運與市區聯營公車、短程客運路線，以及在公有停車場使用。」<br />\n可怕是，目前這種卡已經整合了「借書証」，前不久台北市立圖書館才宣佈<br />\n以後也可以用悠遊卡來借書。可參看新聞：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/7/8/1/n1789433p.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F7%2F8%2F1%2Fn1789433p.htm&d=YnhgAe5tbPrEvEKdRa5CslKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=09fcec52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/7/8/1/n1789433p.htm</a><br />\n而悠遊卡也早整合了「學生証」&darr;<br />\n(<a href=\"http://www.statravel.org.tw/isic/ISICE.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.statravel.org.tw%2Fisic%2FISICE.htm&d=YnhgAe5tbPrEvEKdRa5CslKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=6ff26f6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.statravel.org.tw/isic/ISICE.htm</a>)<br />\n整合的功能愈來愈多和廣。不久這種卡可能就會普及全國，<br />\n並整合成「身分証」、「健保卡」、「駕照」、「提款卡」、「信用卡」等，<br />\n最後政府某一天可能宣佈既然這種卡包含的資料那麼機密和私人，<br />\n萬一卡片遺失了怎麼辦？喔～對了，不如直接以晶片的方式<br />\n注入人體，就可以直接掃描了，也不用擔心卡片會遺失。<br />\n這就是撒但操縱人類的詭計！而那些沒有植入這種晶片的人，<br />\n不能「搭車」(因悠遊卡已經整合在晶片裡」，不能「買東西、賣東西」<br />\n(因為現金制度已被取消，變成電子金錢，而沒有植入晶片就不能買賣)、<br />\n也不能看醫生(因為沒有植入晶片，就等於沒有健保卡)。"},{"pid":"4c6298ce70a0be5fa39a8e5ea57b5cf0a612be0f","tid":900576,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T12:28:50.000Z","msg":"基督教咪就係敵基督"},{"pid":"4cd660f22c83bfa51832ddd66247e2c050f6f2da","tid":900576,"uid":9542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T12:43:16.000Z","msg":"係外國公司做野既支那人都要裝"},{"pid":"31c3b760370e3c7dd4095cf91f1feb8994ce62e5","tid":900576,"uid":36857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"全世界都收窄緊人嘅自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553e52f1ee4c0ee2e01ee4cc5bcf87ad147a4ca8","tid":900576,"uid":145277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T12:51:34.000Z","msg":"連登仔見到植入晶片就忽然耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （雖然我都憎呢樣野）"},{"pid":"9c4db1984e015495d1902bc40aca8a6adbbaff86","tid":900576,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T12:53:45.000Z","msg":"香港班廢老老細會唔會有樣學樣"},{"pid":"c663883da46cb0ab344a7391e4d46d4d330e411c","tid":900576,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T13:05:03.000Z","msg":"用卡都得啦<br />\n點解要晶片"},{"pid":"451ba7d931cdfb31254c6ae8471a85b881193c45","tid":900576,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c663883da46cb0ab344a7391e4d46d4d330e411c","tid":